headline: 2 Large-Cap Stocks Worth Investigating and 1 We Question
summary: Large-cap stocks are known for their staying power and ability to weather market storms better than smaller competitors. However, their sheer size makes it more challenging to maintain high growth rates as they’ve already captured significant portions of their markets.

headline: 3 Reasons to Avoid PRU and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Although Prudential (currently trading at $104.02 per share) has gained 8.6% over the last six months, it has trailed the S&P 500’s 32.7% return during that period. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
